Package: spinifex
Title: Manual tours, manual control of dynamic projections of numeric multivariate data
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nicholas", "Spyrison", email = "spyrison@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Dianne", "Cook", role = c("aut", "ths"))
    )
Description: Generates the path for Manual Tours. Tours are dynamic 
  linear projections of numeric multivariate data (p>3). Implements manual 
  tours, for manual of control of the contributions of the selected variable 
  on the projection space. Additionally allows other tours to be rendered 
  using the 'gganimate' and 'plotly' animation packages.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.4.0),
    tourr
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
